    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for someone who isn't concerned with cosmetic perfection. The exterior shows its age with various scratches, a few small dents, and some clear coat peeling on the roof and trunk. Mechanically, the car is functional and starts consistently, though it will soon require routine maintenance like a tune-up and new tires. The interior remains intact but shows visible wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the carpets, though all power features and the heater work as intended.",
