    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present an automotive specimen of unparalleled quality. This vehicle has been curated to maintain its original showroom integrity, exhibiting an exterior finish and interior upholstery that remain entirely unblemished. Every mechanical system has undergone a comprehensive evaluation to ensure it operates at peak factory specifications. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer to acquire a vehicle that reflects meticulous stewardship and remains in exemplary, preserved condition. We invite you to inspect this definitive example of engineering excellence.",
      "price": 43800.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
