    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this beauty. It\u2019s seriously like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a scratch or a speck on it! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. I'm looking for a quick sale to a good home, so I've priced it to move. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! Let's get you behind the wheel today! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
      "price": 42900.0,
